          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是“二十三岁未曾娶妻”的那个人叫我送来的，小姐请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊红娘，我乃是相国千金，虽然我母亲亏对于他，也不能拿这样的书信戏弄于"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，你对他言讲：倘若禀告老夫人定责不饶，还要打死你这小贱人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么待我去禀告老夫人，打死这小奴才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘我饶了你，你也饶了他吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐“他”是谁啊？谁又是“他”啊？小姐你快些写回信吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与我溶墨。你对张生言讲：我与他写信也不过是问候而已，下次再来书信禀告"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人，定要重责不饶！就是你也要责打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，想人家张先生乃是一片好心，你要是不愿意的话就罢了，你干嘛写这样"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "的信给他，这不是害了他张先生吧！这封信啊，我可不给您送去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小贱子好不知分晓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崔莺莺丢信，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "看小姐做出来许多破绽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "对红娘偏用着要巧语花言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "最可怜背人处红泪偷弹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "还有个痴情种忘废寝餐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "有情人成眷属不羡神仙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张相公开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本来是千金体大家风范"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盼佳期数不清黄昏清旦"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是我愿意儿传书递简"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张珙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听叫门想必是红娘来临，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "但愿得结鸾俦良缘早定。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘姐你来了，小姐怎样言讲？可有书信到来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐看了那封书信就要将我责打，我苦苦地哀求才饶恕了我，叫你妈妈的用功"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "念书，下次再要将书信戏弄于她，禀告老夫人，打死你这小奴才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘姐你要救我一救啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我救不了你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噫！这是小姐的书信，待我三跪九叩香案迎接。哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你打了半天的哈哈，怎么回事啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘姐，这是小姐做的一首好诗啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么好诗啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我念于你听："
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“待月西厢下，迎风户半开。佛墙花影动，疑是玉人来。”"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊好好好！这首诗做得真不错。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊红娘姐，你也明白么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文诌诌的，从头到尾我一句都不懂的，你讲给我听听吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么你要我讲与你听？好！“待月西厢下”就是待月儿上升的时候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，就是月亮上天的时候。张先生，要是阴天没月亮呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，此乃是一句比喻呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，是比喻，那么你往下讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“迎风户半开”就是门儿被风这么一吹么，开了半扇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噢，门儿被风这么一吹，开了半扇儿。张先生，那么它另外半扇怎么不开啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这又是一句比喻呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又是一句比喻，你往下讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“佛墙花影动”就是要跳墙进去与你们小姐相会啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么？我们小姐叫你跳墙相会吗？你说我们小姐多坏啊，表面上庄庄重重的，"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "私底下约人家花园相会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“疑是玉人来”哦哦！！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张先生，谁是玉人啊？玉人又是谁呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是小生我嘛！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哟，敢情你是个玉人啊，我们小姐不是叫你跳墙进去吗？要是把你这个玉人"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摔碎了，可怎么好啊？啊，张先生，既然我们小姐约你今晚跳墙相会，那么你"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就跳吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好便好，只是花园院墙甚高，叫我怎么跳得过去啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这个人哪连狗都不如！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要骂人哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可晓得狗急跳墙，何况人乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红娘下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，这个丫头厉害得很哪！"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "崔莺莺→红娘",
          "turns": 13
