    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第十一场：佳期",
      "characters_present": [
        "崔莺莺",
        "张珙",
        "琴童",
        "红娘"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红娘、崔莺莺同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那夜晚似不该绝人太甚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔莺莺",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "效私奔羞得我小鹿撞心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐别害羞，男大当婚女大当嫁，谁也免不了这回事的，待我叫他开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，妙啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张珙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听叫门想必是小姐来临，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐来了，请啊！哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "请小姐莫负这良辰美景。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，红娘姐，外面有人来了，请你与我看上一看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红娘出，张珙关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张相公，张相公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张珙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘姐，这时候我也顾不得你了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张珙拉崔莺莺同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张相公，张相公！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他们也顾不得我了，想他们双双同入罗帏，竟将我红娘关在门外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张相公，啊张……"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红娘啊红娘，你这算何苦啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（反四平调） 小姐小姐多风采，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君瑞君瑞你大雅才。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "月移花影玉人来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无限的春风抱满怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "柳腰摆，露滴牡丹开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一似襄王神女赴阳台。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这冷露湿透了我的凤头鞋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么我的鞋儿也湿啦，张相公，张相公，你的相思病好了九成了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（琴童上。）"
